---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<article id="skills" class="flex flex-col p-4 justify-center bg-[#2D3E4F] text-[#efefef] min-h-screen">
  <h2 class="text-3xl w-full ">Skills</h2>
  <div tabindex="0" class="collapse collapse-arrow">
    <div class="collapse-title text-xl">Huidige Skillset:</div>
    <p class="collapse-content text-lg">
      Ik ben een autodidact en leer graag in de praktijk. Via <a
        href="https://www.wincacademy.nl"
        target="_blank"
        class="link">WINC Academy</a
      > volg ik de opleiding tot Full Stack Developer. Daarnaast leer ik graag via sites als <a
        href="https://www.udemy.com"
        target="_blank"
        class="link">Udemy</a
      > of via de documentatie van desbetreffende framework, taal, utility.
    </p>
  </div>
  <p class="text-lg pt-4 leading-6 pb-6"></p>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 auto-rows-max">
    <Icon
      name="mdi:language-html5"
      subtext="HTML5"
      size={12}
      color="text-[#e34c26]"
      description="HTML5, semantic HTML, Basics"
    />
    <Icon name="mdi:language-css3" subtext="CSS3" size={12} color="text-[#264de4]" />
    <Icon name="mdi:language-javascript" subtext="JavaScript" size={12} color="text-[#F0DB4F]" />
    <Icon name="mdi:language-typescript" subtext="TypeScript" size={12} color="text-[#007acc]" />
    <Icon name="logos:python" subtext="Python" size={12} />
    <Icon name="carbon:sql" subtext="SQL" size={12} color="text-[#00758F]"/>
    <Icon name="mdi:react" subtext="React" size={12} color="text-[#62DBFB]" />
    <Icon name="simple-icons:redux" subtext="Redux" size={12} color="text-[#764abc]" />
    <Icon name="mdi:git" subtext="Git" size={12} color="text-[#F1502F]" />
    <Icon name="mdi:tailwind" subtext="Tailwind" size={12} color="text-[#38bdf8]" />
  </div>
  <div tabindex="0" class="collapse collapse-arrow pt-6">
    <h3 class="collapse-title text-xl">In Progress:</h3>
    <p class="collapse-content text-lg">Onderstaande talen/frameworks zal ik binnenkort toevoegen aan mijn skillset.</p>
  </div>
   <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 auto-rows-max">
    <Icon name="teenyicons:c-sharp-solid" subtext="C-Sharp" size={12} color="text-[#264de4]" />
    <Icon name="la:node" subtext="NodeJS" size={12} color="text-[#3c873a]" />
    <Icon name="logos:express" subtext="Express" size={12} color="text-[#efefef]" />
   </div>
</article>

